# Test Folder

This folder contains the test files used for the Robotics AI project.

The tests in this folder are mainly included to check the basic quality and structure of the ROS 2 package. They help make sure that the code follows common ROS 2 and Python development standards.

This folder may include the following standard ROS 2 test files:

- `test_copyright.py`
- `test_flake8.py`
- `test_pep257.py`

## Test File Details

### `test_copyright.py`

This test checks whether the source files include the required copyright and license information.

### `test_flake8.py`

This test checks the Python files for coding style issues using `flake8`. It helps keep the code clean, readable, and easier to maintain.

### `test_pep257.py`

This test checks whether the Python docstrings follow the PEP 257 documentation style guidelines.

Overall, this folder supports the project by making sure the ROS 2 package is organized properly and follows basic coding standards.
